1. The Laffer Curve

Domain: economics
Variables: tax rate vs tax revenue

Principle:
	•	Too little pressure → no revenue
	•	Too much pressure → economic activity collapses
	•	Middle zone → maximum productivity

Pantheon analogy

Ethical constraint vs creative output.
	•	Too loose → chaotic outputs
	•	Too strict → refusal paralysis
	•	Balanced → safe but generative reasoning

