Domain: biology, population dynamics

Growth pattern:
	1.	slow start
	2.	exponential growth
	3.	stabilization near carrying capacity

Pantheon analogy

Idea ecosystems or knowledge networks behave similarly.
	•	early exploration phase
	•	rapid conceptual expansion
	•	stabilization when constraints appear

